snippet.title: RECURSOR Announcement Trailer - Live on Kickstarter Now!
snippet.description:
Kickstarter - https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/willsblackett/recursor

RECURSOR is an action roguelite inspired by platform fighters!

Take control of the RECURSOR robot and traverse through a randomly generated labyrinth of trials. Enhance your build by installing a wide variety of upgrades.

Music:
Faster Than Light by Extan
